		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My board allows guest posting, and it gets almost no spam.
<br />How I pulled it off:
<br />* Fake invisible textarea when making a post which spammers fill their text into
<br />* Disallow guests and users with less than 3 posts from posting links
<br />
<br />All that matters is that it's not a stock version of the message board software.

		

